- Database migration: Add `cutting_quote_requests` table

### Success Criteria

- ✅ `POST /public/cutting/quote-request` live on port 3001
- ✅ Rate limiting working
- ✅ Quote requests persisted in DB
- ✅ >10 integration tests passing
